{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6cd4a146a4","title":"读《李氏文集》批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"67c3966f1e","type":"title","text":"读《李氏文集》批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"999603f128","type":"subtitle","text":"读《李氏文集》批语","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"660968fe4c","type":"paragraph","text":"....以善下不争为百谷之王，以好战为乐杀","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"c2b29e34b4","type":"subtitle","text":"件下在一定条人，以用兵为不得已，以胜为不美，以退为进，","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"8d60b45cf3","type":"paragraph","text":"以败为功，以福为福，以得为失，以无知为知，","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"b954dacab1","type":"paragraph","text":"无欲为欲，无名为名。轨谓无为不足以治天下","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"8693d448ec","type":"paragraph","text":"乎？世固未知无为之有益也。[卷十第8页]","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"310b0f12f8","type":"paragraph","text":"身教亦未必","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"efa804c4d3","type":"paragraph","text":"自公倡道以来，谁是接公道柄者乎？他处我皆相与遵守，言不知，新邑是谁继公之真脉者乎？面从而背违，教只要是真理，身教自相与遵守，言教则半句不曾奉行之奖。以亦【未】必没有故我绝不欲与此间人相接，他亦自不与我接。何人奉行。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"},{"id":"b05da89a29","type":"paragraph","text":"者？我无可趋之势故耳。[卷三第16页]","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4"}],"page":{"id":"72a572d65a","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"6cd4a146a4","start":276,"end":276}}}},"__N_SSG":true}